package: Collapse Missing Frames
author: Autodesk, Inc.
organization: Autodesk, Inc.
version: 1.2
rv: 6.0
openrv: 1.0.0
requires: ''
optional: true

modes: 
  - file: collapse_missing_frames.py
    load: immediate

description: |

  <p>This package provides a way to collapse a loaded frame sequence to the frames present on disk by pruning the missing frames with an RVRetime node.</p>

  <p>You will find the per-source option under the Image menu as "Collapse Image Sequence" and the global preference for all sources listed along side as "Collapse All Image Sequences".</p>

